INSTALLATION
========================================





FEATURE SUMMARY
========================================





BUILDING BLOCKS
========================================

Glo is glue.  Today there are many open source software packages available. The
building blocks of Glo are a set of hand picked solutions for each layer in the
stack:

- Apache
- PHP
- Zend Framework
- YUI3
- handlebars



SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS
========================================

Glo's system requirements are defined by the great open source 
software that is the building blocks of Glo.

bash
PHP 5.2.4 or later



INSTALLATION
========================================

* download
* update config file
* $ glo create project Example
* $ sudo ln -s <root>/etc/dev-site.config /etc/apache2/sites-enabled 
* $ sudo /etc/init.d/apache2 restart
* visit your new site in a browser




QUESTIONS AND FEEDBACK
========================================

Online documentation can be found at http://gloframework.com/documentation.
You may also want to visit the forums at http://gloframework.com/forums.
Any bugs that are found should be filed at http://gloframework.com/issues.
If there are issues that can not be resolved in one of the above manners 
please feel email your question to:

feedback@gloframework.com



